01:01:26.330 --> 01:01:28.230
I mean, it sort of
makes sense, because we

01:01:28.230 --> 01:01:29.890
start with the vacuum state.

01:01:29.890 --> 01:01:33.070
And if we squeeze
it, we are not really

01:01:33.070 --> 01:01:35.260
going into the
